        ]
      },
      "level": {
        "value": 5
      },
      "privateNotes": "",
      "publicNotes": "<p><strong>Role:</strong> the muscle of Pilts Swastel's mob — soldiers of the 'Emperor of Old Korvosa,' commanding the petty thugs of Old Dock through fear. Reused throughout the island: street mobs (4), the palace guardroom, the Blood Pig arena (up to 8).</p><p><strong>Tactics:</strong> swarm with battleaxes for flanked Sneak Attacks, hurling throwing axes at runners. <strong>Morale:</strong> bullies at heart — once half their number falls, the rest scatter into the alleys.</p>",
